{"about_the_game":"In this first-person action thriller, play as the hosts of a popular ghost hunting show that is normally staged for views as they discover that this house is truly filled with horrors. Explore a randomly generated mansion, find items to aid you, and kill the spiders infesting the area as you fight to escape <i><strong>The House Where They Dwell</strong></i>.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">EXPLORE THE MANSION</h2>Explore a randomly generated mansion as you collect items to aid you against the mysterious spider infestation!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1759460/extras/Running_Gif.gif?t=1635487332\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">KILL SPIDERS</h2>Watch out! Spiders will increase in size until they are large enough to attack you. Shrink them back down with &quot;SpiderX&quot; Spray and <i>schmack</i> them when they are small enough!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1759460/extras/HoardSpray_Gif.gif?t=1635487332\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1759460/extras/SpiderKill_Gif.gif?t=1635487332\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">DESTROY SPIDER NESTS</h2>Watch out for spider nests throughout the house, they seem to be where the spiders are coming from. Luckily, you can douse the nests and set them ablaze with &quot;Flickers&quot; lighter fluid and matches!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1759460/extras/FluidDouced_Gif.gif?t=1635487332\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1759460/extras/MatchIgnite_Gif.gif?t=1635487332\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1759460/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1635487332","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1759460/page.bg.jpg?t=1